EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0900Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   30 APR THRU 04 MAY IN AREA WITHIN 24 MILES OF
   57-26.8N 008-16.0W. VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER
   AREA SHOULD CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON
   VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 042000Z MAY 18.
